org.zaproxy.zap.extension.websocket.ui

Class WebSocketMessagesViewModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
      • org.zaproxy.zap.extension.websocket.utility.PagingTableModel<WebSocketMessageDTO>
        • org.zaproxy.zap.extension.websocket.ui.WebSocketMessagesViewModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, TableModel
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    WebSocketFuzzMessagesViewModel

    public class WebSocketMessagesViewModel
extends PagingTableModel<WebSocketMessageDTO>
    This model uses the TableWebSocket instance to load only needed entries from database. Moreover it shows only those entries that are not blacklisted by given WebSocketMessagesViewFilter.
